name: Tkined/Scotty
tagline: A Tcl extension for building network management (TCP/IP, HTTP, SNMP, ICMP, UDP, DNS) applications
body:
### Tkined/Scotty
Scotty is a simple to use, low resource network management tool with a graphical interface called Tkined. It monitors devices using a variety of protocols such as tcp/ip snmp and rstatd.
